body:
Imagine this

The avengers are called together to a meeting where Tony announces some relatively sad news.

Peter sighs loudly, looks Tony in the eye and says

“FRIDAY that is so sad play Despacito.”

But that isn’t all. Peter knew Tony would tell FRIDAY to turn it off so he programmed the AI to play the song in its entirety anytime it was asked to play it.

So instead of moving on with the meeting everyone stares at Peter as he mournfully bops to the song.
